                </svg>
                <span>Promotional video played at events (optional)</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-12">
        <p class="text-text-light mb-6">Download our full sponsorship pack for more details, or get in touch to discuss options.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
